be here at the Google Cambridge

00:00:08.480 --> 00:00:09.890
office.

00:00:09.890 --> 00:00:14.000
This is a topic that's very
near and dear to my heart.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:15.830
Growing up as a
nonverbal child--

00:00:15.830 --> 00:00:18.062
I was actually nonverbal
till I was 2 and 1/2

00:00:18.062 --> 00:00:19.520
