00:00:27.140 --> 00:00:33.680
And I want to take a minute
today and really imagine--

00:00:33.680 --> 00:00:38.570
imagine just starting off
with a potential employment

00:00:38.570 --> 00:00:39.690
opportunity.

00:00:39.690 --> 00:00:47.810
And imagine not being able
to get over 1,000 jobs.

00:00:47.810 --> 00:00:52.790
Imagine getting denied
over 1,000 times

00:00:52.790 --> 00:00:56.220
for a meaningful employment.

00:00:56.220 --> 00:00:59.070
Now, that's one of
the extreme cases.

00:00:59.070 --> 00:01:02.030
But that's actually one of
the cases of a young man

00:01:02.030 --> 00:01:04.730
I know who is on the
autism spectrum, who

00:01:04.730 --> 00:01:07.430
has an accounting major,
who graduated college,

00:01:07.430 --> 00:01:10.490
was not able to get
over 1,000 jobs.

00:01:10.490 --> 00:01:12.500
