"Autism and Falling in Love,"

00:03:10.670 --> 00:03:14.240
focus on trying to help
individuals with special needs

00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:16.940
try to find relationships
and love for the first time.

00:03:16.940 --> 00:03:19.604
When I was 18, I had no
idea how to talk to women.

00:03:19.604 --> 00:03:21.020
Pretty sure I still
don't know how

00:03:21.020 --> 00:03:22.860
to talk to women,
for the most part.

00:03:22.860 --> 00:03:25.730
But I wrote this book based
on 10 years of journal entries

00:03:25.730 --> 00:03:27.447
to help some of
my mentees today.

00:03:27.447 --> 00:03:29.780
In addition to that, we've
had the wonderful opportunity

00:03:29.780 --> 00:03:32.000
